sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant P as Parent Sandbox
  participant C as Control Plane
  participant O as Orchestrator
  participant E as Execution Sandbox
  participant S as Object Store
  participant A as Admin Panel

  U->>P: runnerctl run task.toml
  P->>C: submit run request
  C->>C: validate TOML, quota, image, secrets
  C->>O: enqueue run
  O->>E: create execution sandbox
  O->>E: stage inputs and normalized spec
  E->>E: run-agent executes command
  E-->>C: stream logs and metrics
  E-->>S: upload artifacts and manifests
  C-->>A: live state, metrics, cost
  E->>C: final result
  O->>E: destroy sandbox
  C->>S: finalize result bundle
  C-->>U: status, logs, download URL
